<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Antoine Morin — Portfolio</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,500;9..144,600;9..144,700&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}

  :root{
    --paper:      #F6F8FA;
    --paper-soft: #ECF0F4;
    --ink:        #1E2A38;
    --ink-soft:   #5A6B7D;
    --sage:       #4C7A9C;
    --sage-deep:  #335A75;
    --sky:        #7C93A8;
    --apricot:    #5B7A95;
    --sand:       #DCE4EC;
    --line:       rgba(30,42,56,0.10);
    --shadow:     0 18px 40px rgba(30,42,56,0.10);
    --shadow-sm:  0 8px 20px rgba(30,42,56,0.08);
    --radius:     22px;
  }

  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;
    background:var(--paper);
    color:var(--ink);
    overflow-x:hidden;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  h1,h2,h3,.display{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;}
  a{color:inherit;}
  img{display:block;max-width:100%;}
  ::selection{background:var(--sand);}

  /* ---------- ambient background blobs ---------- */
  .ambient{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:-1;overflow:hidden;pointer-events:none;}
  .blob{position:absolute;border-radius:50%;filter:blur(60px);opacity:0.35;}
  .blob1{width:520px;height:520px;background:var(--sage);top:-180px;right:-160px;opacity:0.18;}
  .blob2{width:420px;height:420px;background:var(--sky);top:60vh;left:-180px;opacity:0.16;}
  .blob3{width:380px;height:380px;background:var(--apricot);bottom:-160px;right:10vw;opacity:0.13;}

  /* ---------- nav ---------- */
  nav{
    position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    padding:0 5%;height:76px;
    background:rgba(250,247,241,0);
    transition:background .35s ease, box-shadow .35s ease, backdrop-filter .35s ease;
  }
  nav.scrolled{
    background:rgba(250,247,241,0.85);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    box-shadow:0 1px 0 var(--line);
  }
  .nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2.1rem;list-style:none;}
  .nav-links a{
    font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-soft);
    text-decoration:none;position:relative;padding:0.3rem 0;
    transition:color .2s ease;
  }
  .nav-links a::after{
    content:'';position:absolute;left:0;bottom:-2px;height:2px;width:0;
    background:var(--apricot);transition:width .25s ease;border-radius:2px;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover{color:var(--ink);}
  .nav-links a:hover::after{width:100%;}
  .nav-toggle{display:none;}

  section{padding:7.5rem 5%;position:relative;}
  .wrap{max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;}
  .eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;
    font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.04em;
    color:var(--sage-deep);background:rgba(76,122,156,0.10);
    padding:0.4rem 0.9rem;border-radius:999px;margin-bottom:1.4rem;
  }
  .eyebrow::before{content:'●';font-size:0.55rem;color:var(--apricot);}
  .heading{
    font-size:clamp(2rem,3.6vw,2.85rem);font-weight:600;line-height:1.18;
    color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:1rem;
  }
  .sub{font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--ink-soft);max-width:620px;line-height:1.7;}

  /* ---------- hero ---------- */
  #hero{
    min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;padding-top:76px;
  }
  .hero-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.25fr 0.9fr;gap:4rem;align-items:center;width:100%;
  }
  .hero-grid--solo{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center;justify-content:center;
  }
  .hero-grid--solo .hero-eyebrow{justify-content:center;}
  .hero-grid--solo .hero-actions{justify-content:center;}
  .hero-grid--solo .hero-sub{margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;}
  .hero-eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;
    background:var(--paper-soft);border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:999px;padding:0.5rem 1.1rem;font-size:0.85rem;
    font-weight:600;color:var(--sage-deep);margin-bottom:1.6rem;
  }
  .wave{display:inline-block;animation:wave 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;transform-origin:70% 70%;}
  @keyframes wave{0%,100%{transform:rotate(0deg);}15%{transform:rotate(14deg);}30%{transform:rotate(-8deg);}45%{transform:rotate(14deg);}60%{transform:rotate(0deg);}}
  .hero-title{
    font-size:clamp(3rem,6.4vw,5rem);font-weight:600;line-height:1.05;
    color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:0.9rem;letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  }
  .hero-role{
    font-size:clamp(1.15rem,2vw,1.4rem);font-weight:600;color:var(--sage-deep);
    line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:0.6rem;
  }
  .hero-sub{font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.7;max-width:540px;margin-bottom:2.6rem;font-style:italic;}
  .hero-actions{display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .btn-primary{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;
    padding:0.85rem 1.7rem;border-radius:999px;background:var(--sage-deep);
    color:var(--paper);font-weight:700;font-size:0.92rem;text-decoration:none;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);transition:transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
  .btn-ghost{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;
    padding:0.85rem 1.7rem;border-radius:999px;background:transparent;
    border:1.5px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink);font-weight:700;font-size:0.92rem;
    text-decoration:none;transition:border-color .2s ease, background .2s ease;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--sage);background:rgba(76,122,156,0.06);}


  /* ---------- biography ---------- */
  #biography{background:var(--paper-soft);}
  .fact-row{
    display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:stretch;gap:1.4rem;
    flex-wrap:wrap;margin:2.6rem 0 3.5rem;
  }
  .fact-row .fact{flex:1 1 280px;max-width:320px;}
  .bio-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:0.78fr 1.22fr;gap:3.5rem;align-items:center;}
  .bio-card{
    background:var(--paper);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:2.4rem;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);border:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .bio-card p{font-size:1.02rem;line-height:1.85;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:1.2rem;}
  .bio-card p:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
  .bio-photo-card{
    border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--line);
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);background:var(--sand);padding:10px;
  }
  .bio-photo-card img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/5;object-fit:cover;border-radius:13px;}
  .fact{
    background:var(--paper);border-radius:18px;padding:1.3rem 1.5rem;
    border:1px solid var(--line);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;
  }
  .fact-icon{
    width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .fact-row .fact:nth-child(1) .fact-icon{background:rgba(76,122,156,0.15);}
  .fact-row .fact:nth-child(2) .fact-icon{background:rgba(124,147,168,0.18);}
  .fact-row .fact:nth-child(3) .fact-icon{background:rgba(91,122,149,0.16);}
  .fact-title{font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--ink);}
  .fact-sub{font-size:0.84rem;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:0.1rem;}

  /* ---------- experience (signature thread) ---------- */
  #experience{background:var(--paper);}
  .thread{position:relative;padding-left:2.6rem;}
  .thread::before{
    content:'';position:absolute;left:9px;top:8px;bottom:8px;width:2px;
    background:repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--sage) 0 6px, transparent 6px 12px);
    border-radius:2px;
  }
  .thread-item{position:relative;padding-bottom:3rem;}
  .thread-item:last-child{padding-bottom:0;}
  .thread-dot{
    position:absolute;left:-2.6rem;top:0.3rem;width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--paper);border:3px solid var(--sage);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  }
  .thread-item.current .thread-dot{border-color:var(--apricot);background:var(--apricot);box-shadow:0 0 0 5px rgba(91,122,149,0.18);}
  .thread-card{
    background:var(--paper-soft);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.8rem 2rem;
    border:1px solid var(--line);transition:transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease;
  }
  .thread-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);}
  .thread-period{
    display:inline-block;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--sage-deep);
    background:rgba(76,122,156,0.12);padding:0.25rem 0.75rem;border-radius:999px;margin-bottom:0.7rem;
  }
  .thread-item.current .thread-period{color:var(--apricot);background:rgba(91,122,149,0.14);}
  .thread-role{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:0.2rem;}
  .thread-org{font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:0.9rem;font-weight:500;}
  .thread-desc{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;}
  .thread-desc li{position:relative;padding-left:1.2rem;font-size:0.92rem;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.6;}
  .thread-desc li::before{content:'—';position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--sage);}

  /* ---------- skills & certifications ---------- */
  #skills{background:var(--paper-soft);}
  .skills-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3.5rem;align-items:start;}
  .stamp-list{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0.85rem;align-content:start;}
  .stamp{
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.85rem;min-height:64px;
    font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:700;padding:0.9rem 1.4rem;border-radius:16px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink);background:var(--paper);
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);line-height:1.3;
    transition:transform .18s ease, border-color .18s ease, color .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease;
  }
  .stamp::before{
    content:'';width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;background:var(--sage);
  }
  .stamp:nth-child(3n+2)::before{background:var(--sky);}
  .stamp:nth-child(3n)::before{background:var(--apricot);}
  .stamp:hover{transform:translateX(4px);border-color:var(--sage);color:var(--sage-deep);box-shadow:var(--shadow);}

  .cert-card{
    background:var(--paper);border-radius:16px;padding:1.1rem 1.4rem;
    border:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;align-items:center;
    gap:1rem;margin-bottom:0.85rem;box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);
    transition:transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease;
  }
  .cert-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
  .cert-card:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
  .cert-logo{
    width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:11px;flex-shrink:0;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:#fff;
    background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);overflow:hidden;
  }
  .cert-logo svg{width:26px;height:26px;object-fit:contain;}
  .cert-logo img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;}
  .cert-body{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.3rem;}
  .cert-name{font-weight:700;font-size:0.92rem;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.3;}
  .cert-date{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:600;}
  .cert-date.progress{color:var(--apricot);}
  .badge-progress{
    font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--apricot);background:rgba(91,122,149,0.14);
    padding:0.2rem 0.6rem;border-radius:999px;margin-left:0.5rem;
  }

  /* ---------- resume ---------- */
  #resume{background:var(--paper);}
  .resume-panel{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:0.9fr 1.1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center;
    background:var(--paper-soft);border-radius:28px;padding:3rem;border:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .resume-copy p{color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.6rem;font-size:1rem;}
  .pdf-frame-outer{
    position:relative;border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--line);
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);background:var(--ink);
  }
  .pdf-frame-outer iframe{display:block;width:100%;height:580px;border:none;}

  /* ---------- projects ---------- */
  #projects{background:var(--paper-soft);}
  .projects-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:1.6rem;}
  .project-card{
    background:var(--paper);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:2.1rem;
    border:1px solid var(--line);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);
    transition:transform .22s ease, box-shadow .22s ease;
  }
  .project-card:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
  .project-tag{
    display:inline-block;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--sage-deep);
    background:rgba(76,122,156,0.12);padding:0.28rem 0.75rem;border-radius:999px;margin-bottom:1rem;
  }
  .project-title{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:0.7rem;}
  .project-desc{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.4rem;margin-bottom:1.4rem;}
  .project-desc li{position:relative;padding-left:1.1rem;font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.65;}
  .project-desc li::before{content:'—';position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--sky);}
  .project-tools{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.4rem;}
  .tool-chip{font-size:0.72rem;padding:0.3rem 0.7rem;border-radius:999px;background:var(--sand);color:var(--ink);font-weight:700;}

  /* ---------- contact ---------- */
  #contact{background:var(--ink);color:var(--paper);text-align:center;}
  #contact .eyebrow{background:rgba(250,247,241,0.1);color:var(--sand);}
  #contact .eyebrow::before{color:var(--apricot);}
  #contact .heading{color:var(--paper);}
  #contact .sub{color:rgba(250,247,241,0.7);margin:0 auto 2.4rem;}
  .contact-card{
    max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;background:rgba(250,247,241,0.06);
    border:1px solid rgba(250,247,241,0.14);border-radius:24px;padding:2.6rem;
  }
  .contact-links{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.9rem;margin-bottom:1.6rem;}
  .contact-link{
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.9rem;background:rgba(250,247,241,0.05);
    border:1px solid rgba(250,247,241,0.12);border-radius:14px;padding:1rem 1.3rem;
    text-decoration:none;color:var(--paper);font-weight:600;font-size:0.95rem;
    transition:background .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
  }
  .contact-link:hover{background:rgba(250,247,241,0.1);transform:translateY(-2px);}
  .contact-icon{
    width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(250,247,241,0.12);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .contact-foot{font-size:0.82rem;color:rgba(250,247,241,0.5);}

  footer{
    background:var(--ink);padding:1.6rem 5% 2.4rem;text-align:center;
    border-top:1px solid rgba(250,247,241,0.1);
  }
  .footer-copy{font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(250,247,241,0.45);}

  .fade-up{opacity:0;transform:translateY(26px);transition:opacity .65s ease, transform .65s ease;}
  .fade-up.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}

  @media (max-width:900px){
    .hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .bio-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .bio-photo-card{max-width:280px;margin:0 auto;}
    .skills-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .stamp-list{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .resume-panel{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:2rem;}
    .nav-links{display:none;}
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
    .fade-up{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none;}
    .wave{animation:none;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="ambient">
  <div class="blob blob1"></div>
  <div class="blob blob2"></div>
  <div class="blob blob3"></div>
</div>

<nav id="main-nav">
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#biography">Biography</a></li>
    <li><a href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#resume">Resume</a></li>
    <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- ================= HERO / TITLE ================= -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid hero-grid--solo">
    <div>
      <span class="hero-eyebrow"><span class="wave">👋</span> Based in Ottawa, Canada</span>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Antoine Morin</h1>
      <p class="hero-role">Junior Financial Analyst at DND, serving the CAF</p>
      <p class="hero-sub">Aspiring Master's student.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#biography" class="btn-primary">Get to know me ↓</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/antoine-morin-3a8a161a4/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-ghost">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= BIOGRAPHY ================= -->
<section id="biography">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="fade-up" style="text-align:center;">
      <span class="eyebrow">Who I am</span>
      <h2 class="heading">A bit about me</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="fact-row fade-up">
      <div class="fact">
        <div class="fact-icon">🎓</div>
        <div>
          <div class="fact-title">Telfer School of Management</div>
          <div class="fact-sub">B.Com — Finance &amp; Business Technology, 2027</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fact">
        <div class="fact-icon">📍</div>
        <div>
          <div class="fact-title">Ottawa, Ontario</div>
          <div class="fact-sub">Working across federal departments</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fact">
        <div class="fact-icon">🗣️</div>
        <div>
          <div class="fact-title">Bilingual</div>
          <div class="fact-sub">Fluent in French &amp; English</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bio-grid fade-up">
      <div class="bio-photo-card">
        <img src="2.1 - Profile.jpg" alt="Antoine Morin" />
      </div>
      <div class="bio-card">
        <p>I'm a 4th-year Bachelor of Commerce student at the Telfer School of Management, University of Ottawa, specializing in Finance and Business Technology Management. I'm bilingual with hands-on experience in analytics, ERP systems, and project management across both the federal government and the private sector.</p>
        <p>Right now, I work as a Junior Financial Analyst at DND ADM(MAT), where I help reconcile data, track finances, and prepare reports for a team monitoring contractors, advance payments, and inventory. I've also brought experience as a Web Analytics Officer at Employment and Social Development Canada and as a Software Tester at the Department of National Defence.</p>
        <p>What I love most is turning complex data into something clear and useful — whether that's a Power BI dashboard, an automated workflow, or a well-structured report. I'm always looking to grow in data analytics, public sector finance, and business technology.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= WORK EXPERIENCE ================= -->
<section id="experience">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="fade-up">
      <span class="eyebrow">Where I've worked</span>
      <h2 class="heading">Work Experience</h2>
      <p class="sub">A timeline of roles that shaped how I think about data, systems, and public service.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="thread fade-up" style="margin-top:3rem;">

      <div class="thread-item current">
        <div class="thread-dot"></div>
        <div class="thread-card">
          <span class="thread-period">May 2025 – Present</span>
          <p class="thread-role">Junior Financial Analyst</p>
          <p class="thread-org">Department of National Defence (ADM MAT) · Ottawa, ON</p>
          <ul class="thread-desc">
            <li>Assist with data reconciliation, financial tracking, and report preparation for a team monitoring contractors, advance payments, and inventory.</li>
            <li>Support preparation of monthly, quarterly, semi-annual, and annual financial reports and contribute to Office of the Auditor General audit support.</li>
            <li>Verify information across databases and maintain accurate financial records using SAP, Excel, Access, and Power BI.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="thread-item">
        <div class="thread-dot"></div>
        <div class="thread-card">
          <span class="thread-period">Sept. 2025 – Apr. 2026</span>
          <p class="thread-role">Junior Web Analytics Officer</p>
          <p class="thread-org">Employment and Social Development Canada · Gatineau, QC</p>
          <ul class="thread-desc">
            <li>Support and lead Analytics Services projects, including developing a CRM model and reporting on Adobe Analytics insights to inform business decisions.</li>
            <li>Serve as acting coordinator for client onboarding, managing the full Adobe Analytics solution lifecycle from initiation and testing to launch.</li>
            <li>Apply working knowledge of HTML and JavaScript to interpret metadata and tracking snippets.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

